##
## A propos
##
@node about "About & What is CareTime"

CareTime is here to remind you how long is it working.
I spend to much time on Internet so I decided to code a little
tool to remind me how long I am on the Net.
But you could use it for anything...

The code is based on VLTimer;I only had some little things
The name of the author was not in the source file, but the
source file was free so I use it! Thanks to the author. It
was easy to done CareTime thanks to his job.

So CareTime open a window and give you the time (same as a
clock) and tell you for how long is it lauched by pressing
TAB. Every xx minutes a requester 'll appear to remind you
that you have spend enough time :-) and tell you how much.
It'll produce a logfile which is compatible with PhoneBill
(the log file will be a NComm's log file) and try to under
stand what happend if the amiga crashed for example.

I hope you understand me (my english is not ? brillant ;-)


@endnode


