##
## History
##
@node History History

  V1.0  (18-12-96) First Release.
  V1.1  (19-02-96 internal Realease)
        - can be launch from WB
        - message is not more neccesary
        - a logfile is produced
        - a command can be execute
        - you can give the position of the window
        - it is a commodity so if you lanch it again it will stop
  V1.2b (20-03-96 internal Realease)
        - try to fix some bugs
        - add the possibility to choose the hotkey
  V1.2  (16-04-96) Release on Aminet
        - add a requester that appears on the first log, to tell who
          codes this piece of software :-)
  V1.3  (02-06-96) Release on Aminet
        - caretime didn't unlock the screen, now fixed
        - add NoLog option for people who only want to use caretime
          for its first goal: the timer

@endnode
